Data Fields

EFI_DXE_IPL_ENTRY Entry

Detailed Description

Final service to be invoked by the PEI Foundation. The DXE IPL PPI is responsible for locating and loading the DXE Foundation. The DXE IPL PPI may use PEI services to locate and load the DXE Foundation.
